Saveetha Dental College & Hospitals has global partnerships with international and National Universities/ Industries for academic and research collaborations. The collaboration includes the exchange of faculty, researchers & students, research publications, academic programs, research projects and for conducting joint teaching & research Programmes.

We have joined hands with many international universities/industries across the globe to deliver world class academic and research programmes. We bridge the gap between disciplines and pull through academic and clinical excellence globally. At international level we have built enhancing relationships, country to country programmes crossing the boundaries.
